      "slug": "korea-ai-framework-act-effective-july-21-regulation",
      "category": "AI 监管 · 政策",
      "category_en": "AI Regulation · Policy",
      "title": "韩国AI基本法今日生效：生成式AI标识强制化，全球监管拼图再落一块",
      "title_en": "South Korea's AI Framework Act Takes Effect Today: Mandatory Labeling for Generative AI, Another Piece of the Global Regulatory Puzzle Falls",
      "title_break": "韩国AI基本法今日生效<br>生成式AI强制标识上线",
      "title_break_en": "Korea AI Framework Act Effective Today<br>Mandatory AI Content Labeling Goes Live",
      "deck": "7月21日正式生效，生成式AI内容必须标识、高风险系统需评估、AI公司要设立安全负责人。全球AI监管从"要不要管"进入"怎么管"的细节比拼阶段。",
      "deck_en": "Officially effective July 21 — generative AI content must be labeled, high-risk systems need assessment, AI companies must appoint safety officers. Global AI regulation moves from 'whether to regulate' to 'how to regulate' detail competition.",
      "keywords": "Dawn Vision, 韩国AI基本法, AI监管, 生成式AI, 内容标识, AI安全, 监管政策, 全球AI治理",
      "keywords_en": "Dawn Vision, Korea AI Framework Act, AI regulation, generative AI, content labeling, AI safety, regulatory policy, global AI governance",
      "og_description": "韩国《人工智能基本法》7月21日正式生效，生成式AI内容强制标识、高风险系统评估、安全负责人制度，全球AI监管框架进一步完善。",
      "og_description_en": "South Korea's AI Framework Act officially takes effect July 21, with mandatory generative AI content labeling, high-risk system assessment, and safety officer requirements — global AI regulatory framework further matures.",
      "read_time": "约 5 分钟阅读",
