      "title_break_en": "China Models One-Two US AI Lead<br>Anthropic Valuation Wobbles",
      "deck": "闭源端Kimi K3性能追平GPT-5/Claude，开源端Qwen横扫全球下载量。预测市场上Anthropic万亿估值概率大幅下降——中国AI的追赶速度比想象中更快。",
      "deck_en": "On the closed-source front, Kimi K3 performance matches GPT-5/Claude. On the open-source front, Qwen dominates global downloads. On prediction markets, Anthropic's trillion valuation probability drops sharply — China's AI catch-up is faster than expected.",
      "keywords": "Dawn Vision, 中国大模型, Kimi K3, 月之暗面, Qwen, 阿里千问, Anthropic, 开源模型, AI竞争",
      "keywords_en": "Dawn Vision, Chinese LLMs, Kimi K3, Moonshot AI, Qwen, Alibaba Qwen, Anthropic, open-source models, AI competition",
      "og_description": "中国大模型双杀美国优势：Kimi K3闭源性能追平GPT-5，Qwen开源横扫全球，Anthropic估值预期在预测市场大幅下降。",
      "og_description_en": "Chinese LLMs deliver one-two punch to US AI lead: Kimi K3 closed-source performance matches GPT-5, Qwen open-source sweeps globally, Anthropic valuation drops sharply on prediction markets.",
      "read_time": "约 5 分钟阅读",
