      "slug": "youtube-ai-slop-policy-sony-udio-copyright-lawsuit",
      "category": "AI 新媒体 · 内容创作",
      "category_en": "AI New Media",
      "title": "YouTube整治AI垃圾+Sony起诉Udio 3万首歌：AI内容的版权与质量双收紧",
      "title_en": "YouTube Cracks Down on AI Slop + Sony Sues Udio Over 30K Songs: AI Content Faces Dual Tightening on Copyright and Quality",
      "title_break": "YouTube整治AI垃圾内容<br>Sony起诉Udio 3万首歌",
      "title_break_en": "YouTube Cracks Down on AI Slop<br>Sony Sues Udio Over 30K Songs",
      "deck": "YouTube明确AI垃圾内容不能变现，Sony就3万首歌起诉AI音乐工具Udio。一边是平台在清垃圾，一边是版权方在追债——AI内容的野蛮生长期结束了。",
      "deck_en": "YouTube clarifies AI slop can't be monetized; Sony sues AI music tool Udio over 30,000 songs. Platforms cleaning up garbage on one side, copyright holders collecting debts on the other — the wild growth era of AI content is over.",
      "keywords": "Dawn Vision, YouTube, AI slop, AI垃圾内容, Sony, Udio, AI音乐, 版权诉讼, 内容创作",
      "keywords_en": "Dawn Vision, YouTube, AI slop, AI garbage content, Sony, Udio, AI music, copyright lawsuit, content creation",
      "og_description": "YouTube更新AI垃圾内容变现政策，Sony起诉AI音乐工具Udio涉嫌侵犯3万首歌曲版权，AI内容产业面临版权与质量双重收紧。",
      "og_description_en": "YouTube updates AI slop monetization policy; Sony sues AI music tool Udio for infringing 30,000 songs — AI content industry faces dual tightening on copyright and quality.",
      "read_time": "约 5 分钟阅读",
